 Now firstly, I'm going to show you how much you need for the pants front. You'll need a similar amount, but a bit wider for the pants back.

235
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:42,000
 If you've got wide enough paper, it actually helps to do them side by side, because it means you don't have to draw all of those guidelines, the waist to ankle, the crotch depth again.

