00:22:51,000 --> 00:23:00,000
 So for the front, your paper needs to be approximately 12 inches wider than your thigh measurement, divided by two, that's your upper thigh measurement, one of the measurements we needed.

238
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:08,000
 So take your upper thigh measurement, divided by two, add 12 inches. That is going to give a little bit of room at the sides, we don't want to be scratching around for enough room.

